    "body": "## Summary\n\nReplaces the workspace abstraction with direct org-scope across the entire stack. Organizations are now the single tenant boundary — no more workspace routing, workspace cache, or workspace-level APIs.\n\n### Database & schema\n- Replace all `workspace_*` tables with `org_*` equivalents (migration 0060 — entities, events, integrations, ingest-logs, user-activities, workflow-runs, entity-edges, event-entities)\n- Remove obsolete one-time migration scripts\n- Rename `workspace-names.ts` → `org-names.ts`\n\n### API layer\n- Delete `workspace.ts` tRPC router (~1400 lines) and `user/workspace.ts` (~300 lines)\n- Expand `org/connections.ts`, `org/jobs.ts`; add `org/events.ts`\n- Remove dead `jobs.restart` mutation (empty switch, always throws)\n- Remove JWT bearer auth path from `with-dual-auth` (zero callers, accepted unverified headers)\n- Drop `orgId` from SDK/MCP — API key is already org-scoped in DB, client-supplied org was redundant\n- Remove `MEMORY_API_KEY` and legacy service-auth ingest path (no internal callers)\n- Signal-only logging: remove 3 per-request auth logs, add logs at state-change boundaries\n\n### App routing & UI\n- Remove `[workspaceName]` path segment — sources, events, jobs, settings lifted to `[slug]/(manage)/`\n- Delete workspace creation flow (`/new`) and workspace-switcher component\n- Remove debug panel components (dead code)\n- Replace hardcoded org context with Clerk org lookup for AI agent identity\n- Remove deleted API route stubs (contents, findsimilar, related) that broke the Answer agent\n\n### Platform (Inngest)\n- All pipeline functions (`memory-event-store`, `memory-entity-embed`, `connection-lifecycle`, `ingest-delivery`, `edge-resolver`) migrated from `workspaceId` → `orgId`\n\n### SDK & MCP\n- Update core `lightfast` client and MCP server to org model\n- Remove workspace-related tool factories, validation schemas, and OpenAPI entries\n\n### Packages deleted\n- `app-workspace-cache` (entire package)\n- `app-auth-middleware` (zero imports)\n- `app-test-db` (zero imports, pulled in unused `@electric-sql/pglite`)\n\n### Packages cleaned up\n- `app-validation`: remove workspace forms, schemas, name utils\n- `app-providers`: migrate wire contracts to org scope\n- `app-reserved-names`: remove workspace reserved names\n- `app-ai`: rename `workspace-search` → `org-search`, delete dead workspace tool files\n\n### Code quality\n- Re-enable 10 biome lint rules (28 → 18 disabled), fix all violations\n- Knip cleanup: remove 16 unused deps, 24 unused exports, 21 unused types, 6 dead files\n- Fix stale domain references (`app.lightfast.ai`, `lightfast.com` → `lightfast.ai`)\n- Clean up `knip.json` — remove stale workspaces, add missing ones\n- Complete `workspace` → `org` terminology migration across UI copy, types, and comments\n\n### Docs\n- Rewrite API docs (authentication, errors, overview) for org-scoped auth\n- Rewrite quickstart for org-level onboarding\n- Optimize CodeRabbit config with schema-validated best practices\n\n**Net: −18,753 lines deleted, +11,297 added across 373 files**\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Migration 0060 applies cleanly against staging DB\n- [ ] OAuth connect flow (authorize → callback → poll) completes and stores integration under org\n- [ ] Ingest delivery routes events to correct org tables\n- [ ] Sources/events/jobs pages load under `[slug]/(manage)/`\n- [ ] Search works at org scope\n- [ ] API key auth resolves to org correctly (no X-Org-ID header needed)\n- [ ] Answer agent works without hitting deleted tool stubs\n- [ ] Biome `pnpm check` passes with re-enabled rules\n- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` passes across all workspaces\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
